DotMRPrinter
public class DotMRPrinter.InnerPlan
extends OperatorPlan<DotMRPrinter.InnerOperator>

Helper class to represent the relationship of map, reduce and combine phases in an MR operator. Each MR operator will have an inner plan of map -> (combine)? -> (reduce)? inner operators. The inner operators contain the physical plan of the execution phase.
